'''霍士河州立監獄'''（{{lang-en|Fox River State Penitentiary}}）是美國電視連續劇《[[越狱_(电视剧)|逃]]》第一季中虛構的一所[[美國監禁制度#安全級別|最高安全級別]]監獄。該監獄在現實世界中的拍攝地其實是{{link-en|喬利埃特監獄|Joliet Correctional Center}}，位於美國[[伊利諾伊州|伊利諾伊州]]的[[喬利埃特_(伊利諾州)|喬利埃特]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/travel/20131109/tc09route66/zh-hant/|title=66號公路之旅：從「越獄」到林肯|author=衛西諦|date=2013-11-09|newspaper=紐約時報中文網|accessdate=2018-10-17|language=zh-hant |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404113700/https://cn.nytimes.com/travel/20131109/tc09route66/zh-hant/ |archive-date=2019-04-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==拍攝==
喬利埃特監獄於1858年建成，2002年關閉，拍攝工作在空置的監獄中進行，由於其濃厚的歷史背景，該劇的製片人[[保羅·舒爾靈|保羅·舒爾靈]]甚至將監獄本身形容為一個角色。<ref name=chicagotribune>{{cite web|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/chi-050824prisonbreak,0,1650127.story |title=Joliet prison is a 'Break'-out star|date=2005-08-24|access-date=2021-07-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051124081941/http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/chi-050824prisonbreak,0,1650127.story |archive-date=2005-11-24 |publisher=Chicago Tribune|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/9981954/ |title=Joliet is one of the characters on 'Prison Break'|publisher= [[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]| date=2005-11-09| access-date=2021-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051202234822/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/9981954/|archive-date=2005-12-02 |dead-url=yes}}</ref>

